00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:10.920
our eyes when we’re tired?”

00:00:10.920 --> 00:00:14.300
I don’t know if you know this, bored during
school, but your username goes really well

00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:17.360
with your question. Maybe you do know, maybe
